{"type":null,"faqId":38431,"title":"管理联系人","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>1. 创建联系人</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125178\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“联系人”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125179\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在弹出的选项菜单选择联系人的存储位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>输入联系人姓名、电话号码等信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125180\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>2. 编辑联系人 </span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125181\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“联系人”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>长按要更新的联系人，然后点击“编辑”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>编辑联系人的信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125182\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>3. 删除联系人</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125183\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“联系人”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125184\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 删除”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>选择要删除的联系人，或点击“全选”选择所有联系人。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125185\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“删除”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3692","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441434792000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":85,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"管理联系人","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}